parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the vehicle is hard to steer
the steering wheel locks up
and loud noises are heard when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the vehicle is hard to steer
the steering wheel locks up
and loud noises are heard when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering alignment system can cause the vehicle to pull to one side, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
and the vehicle is hard to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the inner tie rod can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the vehicle is hard to steer
and loud noises are heard when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause injuries, accidents, or distractions while driving.
symptoms: Airbags deployed without a crash
while the vehicle was parked or in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dashboard Cracks and Airbag Safety Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracks in the dashboard can compromise the integrity of the airbag system, leading to improper deployment or failure to deploy.
symptoms: Cracks appeared on the dashboard
particularly around the airbag compartment
without any apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard near the airbag can potentially compromise the proper deployment of the airbag, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Cracks or splits on the dashboard near the passenger-side airbag
often on either side of the airbag or along the crease designed to break when the airbag deploys.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A broken door handle can make it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door handle is broken
making it hard to open the door.
